Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:45.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to \Nthe sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:07.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:07.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has \Nfaded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:12.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:12.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separated from the rest of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy has rushed to Marineford,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,scene of a battle between the \NWhitebeard Pirates and the Navy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to rescue his brother, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, all ships and soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you are all set, we \Nmove the schedule forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and execute Ace immediately. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy-kun...\N--Let's move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's not the side!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, don't tell me that's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all! Who is in that lineup?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All forces are here on both sides! \NThere are a lot of big names!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's got to be ready for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, we're coming to rescue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garp! It's your family again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The grandson of the hero--Garp and \Nthe son of the revolutionary--Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of him for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Croco boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I think he chickened out and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went ahead of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we are here, our \Nagreement has been fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want to protect Whitebeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought--this old man is Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then leave him alone! Ace likes this old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace's brother is quite a fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came here to rescue your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who you're messing with?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A squirt like you will be dead meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! That's not up to you to decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you're up to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna \Nbecome the King of the Pirates, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.24,0:06:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm the one who'll become the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How saucy you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:07:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you if you \Ncause me trouble, spoiled brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna do as I like!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna rescue Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Even If It Means Death! Luffy \Nvs. the Navy; The Battle Starts!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the... rookie--Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does he know Whitebeard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should hide after \Nbreaking out of the great prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why bother coming to this living hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Because he is Luffy-san.\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he is Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Old man.\N--Hmmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard while on a Navy ship that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a bonehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish he'd just get his \Nass kicked already! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How brave he is! Only his son could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're gonna execute Ace immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they would  after getting \N"all set" for something...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but they were using codes  \Nso I couldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you wanna rescue Ace, too, \Nso I wanted to share that with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That was important information.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can he talk on equal \Nterms with Whitebeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Ace, I'm coming now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he so confident?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he is Ace's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep up with the boy! Let's go, 3rd division!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,14th division, let's charge ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Commander Jill!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so encouraged by just one daredevil?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But our strategy is airtight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hesitate! Do as I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Sengoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he thinks that he doesn't need
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to stick \Nto the schedule for the execution of a mere pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key is--after they're "all set" for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops! I heard that they're \Nmoving Ace's execution forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard. How're Squard and the others doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're tied up with the vice admirals at \Nthe bay head. I'm gonna fly there and help...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it must be a part of his plan that \Nwe'd get some leaked information and advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sengoku wouldn't let his enemy \Nknow his strategy so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not that foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A kick at the speed of light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push your luck. I won't \Nlet you invade that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Admiral Kizaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the guy from Sabaody!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I was gonna ruin you there because \Nthe Celestial Dragons wanted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Straw Hat is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Wink!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I wanna go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What, Captain Buggy?!\N--I can't believe what you just said!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you wanna destroy Kizaru \Nquickly so you can rush home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only a legendary pirate could \Nface Admiral Kizaru without fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are too positive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw boy, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close! Thanks, Ivan-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My only mission is to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kizaru, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.01,0:11:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No, it's not! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the bear-like guy who blew us all away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rolling Spa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bartholomew Kuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How despicable you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you have a \Nrole as a Warlord but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we've known each other so long. \NHow can you just fire a laser at me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how could you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ivan-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me and just go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so unlucky of you to run into us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat, you're gonna die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Fullbody!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta pay for what happened at \Nthe on-the-sea restaurant--Baratie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sanji beat you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should remember this chakram.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the hypnotist from Usopp's \Nvillage. Why're you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I honed my skill in the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.42,0:13:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With two chakrams, it's twice as effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I say "one, two, Django," \Nyou're gonna get tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Django!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you from Alabasta, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no time to play with you people now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get away! Kimono Sleeve Cage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will bind anyone who passes through me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's her signature phrase!\N--Miss Hina is so captivating!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of being in bars! Second Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was fast! I couldn't see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We failed, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're bound by Miss Hina--body and soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:47.03,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE BAY HEAD OF MARINEFORD
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight the vice admirals \Nalone! They'll defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Squard! It's getting \Nfrantic inside the bay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta hurry up and get to Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wall that Oars broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I sneak in from here, \Nmaybe I can outsmart them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! He's high-spirited as usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! I'll cut his shadow off \Nand implant it in Oars again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, zombie soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, zombie soldiers! \NGo ahead and capture Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria! I don't wanna deal with him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your bullets back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're multiplying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because this is a battlefield and and \Nall the corpses provide fresh zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Capture Straw Hat!\N--He's the main suspect of the escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got to fight all these officers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how long he can hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're both pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We both sailed on the sea as we liked!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my own adventures!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my own friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...keep your hands off of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wimp like you wants to save me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that I'll allow you to do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so humiliating!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back, Luffy! Why did you come here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:19:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you, Luffy! I don't \Nwant you to share my fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.76,0:19:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can become brothers \Nif we exchange this cup of sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, we're brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Did he just say "I'm your brother?"\N--He's also a son of Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Ace was born, both of his \Nparents died. That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn about...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the rules of pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hardhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:20:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, zombie soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seawater?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.41,0:20:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, Moria, your \Nzombie soldiers can't take salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy-kun, let me handle them!\N--Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--"First Son of the Sea" Jimbei!\N--The former Warlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Don't let this \Nrookie take control of the war!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna crush him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's also a loose cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He grew up together with \NAce as his step-brother
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's a biological son \Nof the revolutionary Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The revolutionary Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The worst criminal in history?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sounds very familiar!\N--His daddy's got such a big name!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He revealed it!\N--Luffy-san...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't care less even \Nif you were the devil's son!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.33,0:21:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That explains everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Gum-Gum Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understand  what \Nhappened at Loguetown!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Dragon saved Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They mean that Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head Office! I'm calling from \NSabaody! We've got big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spread this all over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't allow him to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.22,0:22:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares? There's no need to hide it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That label won't hurt him because \NLuffy is already a notorious outlaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brothers are both fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.13,0:22:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.36,0:22:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Giant...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.24,0:22:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.08,0:22:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna save you even if it means death!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That brat!\N--We all feel the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.39,0:23:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We're Ace's family, too!\N--We're gonna save him at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.36,0:23:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marco, we can't let that kid die.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.82,0:23:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.49,0:23:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.51,0:23:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the Whitebeard Pirates \Ncontinue to run forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.66,0:23:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As he watches his friends face off \Nagainst foes with awesome powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace comes to a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.30,0:23:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, the Navy enacts a new plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.93,0:23:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hard Battles, One After Another! Devil \NFruit Eaters vs. Devil Fruit Eaters!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.68,0:23:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
